aygun, 37, became something of a global laughing stock after her unorthodox routine, including kangaroo hops and imitating a sprinkler, failed to impress the judges at the games.\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.8368637938660813e-20, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 376}, {\"ngram\": \"a global laughing stock\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 403}, {\"ngram\": \"her unorthodox routine\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"kangaroo hops\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 457}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprinkler\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 503, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her moves were copied on late-night talk shows and her unfashionable green tracksuit was mercilessly parodied online.\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her moves\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 538}, {\"ngram\": \"late-night talk shows\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"her unfashionable green tracksuit\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunntold Sydney radio she was still breaking but not competing.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am not going to compete any more,\\\" she told Australian radio station 2DayFM on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 760, \"end\": 770, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.45155133403789527, \"rank\": 0.6736692600927111, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_national_cricket_team\", \"d